# Repo Health Checker

![CI](https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/repo-health-checker/actions/workflows/check.yml/badge.svg)

Automatic repo health check system. Every push-la GitHub Actions check.sh run pannudhuu.

## What It Checks

- README.md exists and has more than 5 lines
- .gitignore is present
- No secret or .env files are committed
- All commit messages have more than 5 words
- CI workflow file exists
- No files over 5MB are committed